## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all cultural contexts or recent developments in the field. The studies referenced primarily focus on Western and some Asian cultures, potentially limiting the applicability of conclusions to other cultural settings. Additionally, the dynamic nature of culture and ethics means that ongoing research is necessary to capture evolving trends and insights.